{"tid":1681704,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黎巴嫩總理在全國示威爆發13日後宣布辭職","createTime":"2019-10-29T15:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T15:04:18.000Z","uid":263926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a9b9cb6e4743c0baa051acad2fd1a19041527442","tid":1681704,"uid":263926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T15:01:00.000Z","msg":"示威不斷 黎巴嫩總理請辭<br />\n<br />\n在黎巴嫩爆發13天來的全國示威之後，總理哈里里(Saad Hariri)今天(29日)宣布辭職。<br />\n<br />\n黎巴嫩債台高築，正面臨嚴重經濟危機，銀行已經關閉多日。<br />\n<br />\n哈里里表示，他已經在今天，向總統奧恩(Michel Aoun)提出政府總辭，同時呼籲，保護國內和平。<br />\n<br />\n由於黎巴嫩政府決定，針對人民使用網路通訊軟體Whatsapp通話，也需要向政府交稅，引發這一波示威。<br />\n<br />\n這次黎巴嫩歷史性抗議浪潮是針對政治人物，他們因腐敗及帶領國家走向經濟崩潰受到指責。示威民眾要求政府下台。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2039616\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2039616&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2BsgzIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=059f2f20\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2039616</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-10-29/lebanon-s-prime-minister-hariri-says-to-resign-amid-unrest\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-10-29%2Flebanon-s-prime-minister-hariri-says-to-resign-amid-unrest&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2BsgzIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=275913db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-10-29/lebanon-s-prime-minister-hariri-says-to-resign-amid-unrest</a><br />\n<br />\n林奠你幾時辭職呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c26c9cf1f2d7c626f77fc03806e9a200d0e8bb","tid":1681704,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T15:01:19.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img 